data.value: SELECT CLI_FE.CVE_VENDEDOR, (SELECT NOMBRE FROM VENDEDORES WHERE CLAVE=CLI_FE.CVE_VENDEDOR) VENDEDOR, NVL(CLI_FE.FE_ART_CANTIDAD,0) FE_ART_CANTIDAD, NVL(CLI_FE.FE_IMPORTE,0) FE_IMPORTE, NVL(NC.NC_ART_CANTIDAD,0) NC_ART_CANTIDAD, NVL(NC.NC_IMPORTE,0) NC_IMPORTE, NVL(CLI_FE.FE_IMPORTE,0) - NVL(NC.NC_IMPORTE,0) VENTA FROM ( SELECT VEND.VEND_CLAVE CVE_VENDEDOR, NVL(FE.FE_ART_CANTIDAD,0) FE_ART_CANTIDAD, NVL(FE.FE_IMPORTE,0) FE_IMPORTE FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT(VEND_CLAVE) VEND_CLAVE FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT(FE.VEND_CLAVE) VEND_CLAVE FROM FACTURAS_EMITIDAS FE,DETALLES_FACTURAS_EMITIDAS DFE WHERE FE.NUMERO = DFE.FACT_EM_NUMERO AND FE.FOLFAC_FOLIO = DFE.FACT_EM_FOLFAC_FOLIO AND DFE.ALM_CLAVE IN(4) AND TRUNC(FE.FECHA) BETWEEN TO_DATE('01/09/2015','DD/MM/YYYY') AND TO_DATE('10/09/2015','DD/MM/YYYY') UNION SELECT DISTINCT(NC.VEND_CLAVE) VEND_CLAVE FROM NOTAS_CREDITO_AL_CTE NC, DETALLES_NOTAS_CREDITO_AL_CTE DNC WHERE NC.NUMERO=DNC.NCR_AL_CTE_NUMERO AND NC.FOL_NCR_CT_FOLIO = DNC.NCR_AL_CTE_FOL_NCR_CT_FOLIO AND DNC.ALM_CLAVE IN(4) AND TRUNC(NC.FECHA) BETWEEN TO_DATE('01/09/2015','DD/MM/YYYY') AND TO_DATE('10/09/2015','DD/MM/YYYY') ) WHERE VEND_CLAVE IS NOT NULL ) VEND LEFT JOIN ( SELECT FE.VEND_CLAVE, NVL(SUM(DFE.CANTIDAD),0) FE_ART_CANTIDAD, NVL(SUM(DFE.PRECIO*DFE.CANTIDAD),0) FE_IMPORTE FROM DETALLES_FACTURAS_EMITIDAS DFE, FACTURAS_EMITIDAS FE WHERE FE.FOLFAC_FOLIO=DFE.FACT_EM_FOLFAC_FOLIO AND FE.NUMERO=DFE.FACT_EM_NUMERO AND DFE.ART_CLAVE <> 'SEGURO' AND FE.STATUS_CAN='N' AND DFE.ALM_CLAVE IN(4) --AND INSTR(','||COALESCE('1,1023',TO_CHAR(FE.VEND_CLAVE))||',',','||FE.VEND_CLAVE||',')!=0 AND TRUNC(FE.FECHA) BETWEEN TO_DATE('01/09/2015','DD/MM/YYYY') AND TO_DATE('10/09/2015','DD/MM/YYYY') GROUP BY FE.VEND_CLAVE )FE ON VEND.VEND_CLAVE = FE.VEND_CLAVE )CLI_FE LEFT JOIN ( SELECT NC.VEND_CLAVE, NVL(SUM(DNC.CANTIDAD),0) NC_ART_CANTIDAD, NVL(SUM(DNC.PRECIO*DNC.CANTIDAD),0) NC_IMPORTE FROM DETALLES_NOTAS_CREDITO_AL_CTE DNC,NOTAS_CREDITO_AL_CTE NC WHERE DNC.NCR_AL_CTE_FOL_NCR_CT_FOLIO=NC.FOL_NCR_CT_FOLIO AND DNC.NCR_AL_CTE_NUMERO = NC.NUMERO AND TRUNC(NC.FECHA) BETWEEN TO_DATE('01/09/2015','DD/MM/YYYY') AND TO_DATE('10/09/2015','DD/MM/YYYY') AND NC.TIPO IS NULL AND NC.STATUS_CAN='N' AND DNC.ALM_CLAVE IN(4) --AND INSTR(','||COALESCE('1,1023',TO_CHAR(NC.VEND_CLAVE))||',',','||NC.VEND_CLAVE||',')!=0 AND (NC.CONC_NOT_CLAVE=4 or NC.CONC_NOT_CLAVE=5 OR NC.CONC_NOT_CLAVE = 19 OR NC.CONC_NOT_CLAVE = 20 OR NC.CONC_NOT_CLAVE = 21 OR NC.CONC_NOT_CLAVE = 34 ) GROUP BY NC.VEND_CLAVE ) NC ON CLI_FE.CVE_VENDEDOR = NC.VEND_CLAVE
